nodes.name: Fil_KODuplicated
nodes.description:
Select the repeated data in the file using:
Indentificador_legal_customer
Country
internalRepresentUser

configuration.sql:
SELECT 
	DISTINCT trace_id, companyId, country, internalRepresentUser
FROM 
	Sel_CompanyCountryUser
WHERE CONCAT(companyId, country, internalRepresentUser) IN (
  SELECT 
	CONCAT(companyId, country, internalRepresentUser)
FROM 
  Sel_CompanyCountryUser
 WHERE
  	 companyId IS NOT NULL
 	 AND country IS NOT NULL
  	 AND internalRepresentUser IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY companyId,country,internalRepresentUser
HAVING count(CONCAT(companyId, country,internalRepresentUser)) > 1
)

	trace_id

nodes.name: Fil_QRLegalCustomer
nodes.description:
QR_1: Null_country
QR_2: Null_agent
QR_3: Null_entity
QR_4: Null_companyName
QR_5: Null_companyId
QR_6:Format_companyStartDate
ISO 8601 'YYYY-MM-DD'
QR_7:Format_companyEndDate
ISO 8601 'YYYY-MM-DD'
QR_8:Domain_countryIncorporation
ISO 3166-alpha 2 
QR_9:Domain_companyType
ISIC codes reference
-- pending isic code description

configuration.sql:
SELECT
	  'Null_country' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_LegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  country IS NULL 
UNION 
  SELECT
	  'Null_agent' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_LegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  agent IS NULL 
UNION
  SELECT
	  'Null_entity' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_LegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  entity IS NULL 
UNION
  SELECT
	  'Null_companyName' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_LegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  companyName IS NULL 
UNION
  SELECT
	  'Null_companyId' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_LegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  companyId IS NULL 
UNION
  SELECT
	  'Format_companyStartDate' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
  FROM
	  Sel_LegalCustomer
  WHERE
	  companyStartDate IS NOT NULL AND
	  companyStartDate NOT rlike '^([0-9]{4})\-(0[1-9]|1[012])\-(0[1-9]|[12][0-9]|3[01])$'
UNION
  SELECT
	  'Format_companyEndDate' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
  FROM
	  Sel_LegalCustomer
  WHERE
	  companyEndDate IS NOT NULL AND
	  companyEndDate NOT rlike '^([0-9]{4})\-(0[1-9]|1[012])\-(0[1-9]|[12][0-9]|3[01])$'
UNION
  SELECT
	  'Domain_countryIncorporation' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
  FROM
	  Sel_LegalCustomer
  WHERE
	  countryIncorporation IS NOT NULL AND
	  countryIncorporation NOT IN (
		SELECT iso2 FROM in_XD_raw_ref_countries)
UNION
  SELECT
	  'Domain_companyType' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
  FROM
	  Sel_LegalCustomer
  WHERE
	  companyType IS NOT NULL AND
	  companyType NOT IN (
		SELECT code FROM in_XD_raw_ref_isic_code)

nodes.name: Fil_QRUserLegalCustomer
nodes.description:
QR_1:Null_firstName
QR_2:Null_lastName
QR_3:Null_documentType
QR_4:Null_countryDocument
QR_5:Null_documentNumber
QR_6:Null_cmc
QR_7:Null_internalRepresentUser
QR_8:Null_contactDataMail
QR_9:Null_contactDataMOBI
QR_10:Domain_documentType
Possible values are:
1 = National ID card 
2 = Passport 
3 = Child's ID card

SELECT
	  'Null_firstName' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_UserLegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  firstName IS NULL 
UNION 
  SELECT
	  'Null_lastName' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_UserLegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  lastName IS NULL 
UNION 
   SELECT
	  'Null_documentType' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_UserLegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  documentType IS NULL 
UNION 
   SELECT
	  'Null_countryDocument' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_UserLegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  countryDocument IS NULL 
UNION 
   SELECT
	  'Null_documentNumber' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_UserLegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  documentNumber IS NULL 
UNION 
   SELECT
	  'Null_cmc' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_UserLegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  cmc IS NULL 
UNION 
   SELECT
	  'Null_internalRepresentUser' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_UserLegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  internalRepresentUser IS NULL 
UNION 
   SELECT
	  'Null_contactDataMail' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_UserLegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  contactDataMail IS NULL 
UNION 
   SELECT
	  'Null_contactDataMOBI' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_UserLegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  contactDataMOBI IS NULL 
UNION 
   SELECT
	  'Domain_documentType' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_UserLegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  documentType not between 1 and 7
UNION 
   SELECT
	  'Domain_typeDisposition' as internal_status,
	  trace_id
   FROM
	  Sel_UserLegalCustomer
   WHERE
	  typeDisposition not in ("JOINT","SINGLE")

Possible values are:

BBA - Local format

	  trace_id

nodes.name: Un_processLog
nodes.description: Union all logs.

nodes.name: Sel_ProcessLog
nodes.description: Select only non duplicated fields. (to avoid duplicated registers by trace id)

configuration.sql:
SELECT 
trace_id as traceId,
collect_set(struct(
      log as levelLogId,
  	  qa_error as errorId,
  	  description,
      current_timestamp() as stepTimestamp,
  	  struct(status as statusId) as onboardingStatus,
  	  struct(step as stepId) as onboardingStep,
   	  struct(error as mainErrorId) as onboardingError
)) as onboardingProcessLogs
from Un_processLog
group by trace_id
